Package: mr
Type: Package
Title: Generate, Show and Play Musical Score in R Markdown, RStudio or Browser
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Renfei Mao
Maintainer: Renfei Mao <renfeimao@gmail.com>
Description: An elegant and intuitive system for representing musical scores,
    and generating and displaying them painlessly in R Markdown or RStudio.
    You only tell "mr" the structure of your music, and it takes care of all
    the dirty technical details.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
